AI-Driven Adaptive Quiz System with Intelligent Anti-Cheating Detection for Improving College Learning and Assessment at South East Asian Institute of Technology

drivin - use ai to make decisions automatically 

adaptive - the qiuz change depending on student performance.

 FEATURES:
1. Instructor Quiz Builder
Create multiple choice / identification / short answer
Set time limit
Randomize questions
Auto-grading system

2. Listening-Based Quiz Mode
Question binabasa via Smart TTS
Adjustable speed
Option to replay
Highlight habang binabasa

3. AI Performance Analysis
Detect weak topics
Suggest review materials
Identify frequent mistakes

4. Suspicious Behavior Pattern Detection
AI analyzes:
Extremely fast answering time
Sudden perfect score after previous low scores
Identical answer pattern between students
Multiple tab switching behavior
Student answers 30 questions in 1 minute

5. Adaptive Question Randomization
AI:
Shuffles question order
Changes question difficulty
Randomizes choices


